text: "Diva" is a 2009 song by Beyoncé and is third single from her third studio album I Am... Sasha Fierce (2008), along with "Halo". It went to number 1 in Brazil, number 19 in the United States, number 26 in New Zealand, number 40 in Australia, number 50 in Ireland, number 60 in South Korea, number 72 in the United Kingdom and number 73 in the Netherlands. title: Diva (Beyoncé song)
